<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Password Reset</h1>
    <p>Dear User,</p>
    <p>We have received a request to reset your password. To proceed, please click on the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= it.resetUrl %>">Reset Password</a></p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
</body>
</html>